{"id": "1199449547932450878", "channel_id": "1199449547932450878", "type": 0, "author_id": "870225701855436801", "author_name": "ahuahuahua", "author_bot": false, "content": "在防禦卡上使用偶然謬誤後，該防禦卡將會視為打擊，但是這張防禦卡似乎會失去防禦的特性，無法觸發冒險的行囊或核心熔解等等效果，請問這是正常設定嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-01-23T20:24:16.922000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🪦", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199449547932450878", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」在防禦卡上使用偶然謬誤", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1199271061355761734", "channel_id": "1199271061355761734", "type": 0, "author_id": "660863943715192832", "author_name": "milktea_0115", "author_bot": false, "content": "只有沒辦法關注我女友,按關注按了好幾次,關注其他人都沒問題\n而且每次切頁面那個助戰喚醒體都會不一樣\n狀態也都不一樣", "timestamp": "2024-01-23T08:35:02.406000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-23T08:35:21.646000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1199271061670330439", "filename": "2024-01-23_163222.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 119044, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1199271061355761734/1199271061670330439/2024-01-23_163222.png?ex=6a004336&is=69fef1b6&hm=453bc9544c793b53e65451a400848d5ed82abecdcc671424bbb5e65c161bf79b&"}, {"id": "1199271061959749643", "filename": "2024-01-23_163259.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 113298, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1199271061355761734/1199271061959749643/2024-01-23_163259.png?ex=6a004336&is=69fef1b6&hm=f17fc66dd5257834580d44aed7baa14186b5f5f7cd8d05989517e8fc83492f89&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199271061355761734", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」無法關注人", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1199347038450634862", "channel_id": "1199347038450634862", "type": 0, "author_id": "998266367650308108", "author_name": "banano.2", "author_bot": false, "content": "幫朋友問的\n25等了還顯示24等🥲 領不了\n等級已經25等了", "timestamp": "2024-01-23T13:36:56.757000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-23T13:37:15.683000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1199347039042011239", "filename": "Screenshot_20240123-223338.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2211065, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1199347038450634862/1199347039042011239/Screenshot_20240123-223338.png?ex=6a0089f8&is=69ff3878&hm=6f21934a31519d05401a135494875bd54536f8f3c9db9c850cdc1d5f36895b5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199347038450634862", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」25等獎勵領不了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1199301697051299940", "channel_id": "1199301697051299940", "type": 0, "author_id": "1183805648929042473", "author_name": "shuaidaobaole", "author_bot": false, "content": "我关注到第200个人之后，无论再怎么点都提示“客户端传入数据错误”，明明追随者没有200上限的。", "timestamp": "2024-01-23T10:36:46.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199301697051299940", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」为什么关注上限只有200", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1199274107565506560", "channel_id": "1199274107565506560", "type": 0, "author_id": "1193429045824717004", "author_name": "xiaomaoshishenme", "author_bot": false, "content": "为啥要强行拉到到 后期。\n\n本来循环起来靠的就是狂气充能。出爆发。\n再加上回合限制。\n\n实在想不通后期才生成正常狂气的原因\n\n为了升级而升级的设计吗。\n\n后期可以添加伤害。但是狂气不是开始给满 实在托节奏。", "timestamp": "2024-01-23T08:47:08.679000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199274107565506560", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」技能的增加狂气 直接一级给满不行吗？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1199246133101334578", "channel_id": "1199246133101334578", "type": 0, "author_id": "1079677800023347250", "author_name": "juzi6912", "author_bot": false, "content": "比如某位角色可以直接購買的課金項，等一年進入普池真的太久了，而且資源不太好攢，對於臉黑的玩家來說，雙池二百左右限定抽真的太痛苦了😢現在本人月卡和課題都課金了，禮包328以下的也都買了一遍，可是還是擔憂未來的抽卡（很擔憂），畢竟遇到很喜歡的角色，卻抽不到，真的會成為遺憾😞\n像我這類非養成類的卡牌玩家更喜歡直接買，就當作DLC擴充了🥰考慮到流水，可以在檔期池子之後的一兩個月內上線角色的DLC擴充包以及相關命輪的擴充包，這樣對之後新入遊戲的新人也有很大幫助，這樣官方可以認真考慮一下嗎\n再一個就是會有皮膚之類的上架嗎？還挺期待的😘（個人想法，不喜勿噴）\n真的很喜歡這個遊戲，希望未來越來越好🥰\n@game.producer.light#0 @手動@官方", "timestamp": "2024-01-23T06:55:59.047000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199246133101334578", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」請問之後是否可以添加類似的課金項", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
